title: Concorde For Microsoft Flight Simulator FS9 & FSX
description:
The Concorde for MSFS 2004 & FSX.

The sound.cfg file is set to use the default soundpack for the B734 in FS9, but in FSX will default to the "stock" propeller sound in FSX, so you should add a soundpack. The are many good sources for the soundpack. Simply do a Google search, and you should be able to find it. 

Date: 11-05-2008

FS2004/FSX Concorde Collection. Includes model, textures, VC, passenger views, 
fully animated parts, instructions for gauges on FSX cockpit / VC mode. Gauges not included.

Reupload from 2013

Have Phun
